Required dependencies:
----------------------
- Camomile version 0.8.3 <http://camomile.sourceforge.net/>
- Camlzip version 1.04 <http://forge.ocamlcore.org/projects/camlzip/>

Installation steps:
-------------------
sh configure [-ocaml-prefix <path>] # same path as passed to OCaml ./configure
make all
make install # may require root privileges, use 'sudo make install'
